Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.cli.components

package it.polimi.ingsw.client.cli.components
Classes that implement the graphical components of the command-line interface of the client of the Masters of Renaissance game.
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    ActionToken
    Cli component that gives a string representation of action tokens.
    Box
    Cli component that boxes other components, by adding borders to their string representation.
    DevCardColor
    Cli component that represents card colors as bold and colored strings.
    DevCardGrid
    Cli component that gives a string representation of the development card grid.
    DevCardRequirement
    Cli component that gives a string representation of development cards requirements.
    DevelopmentCard
    Cli component that gives a string representation of a development card.
    DevSlots
    Cli component that gives a string representation of a development card player slot.
    FaithTrack
    Cli component that gives a string representation of the faith track.
    LeaderBoard
     
    LeaderCard
    Cli component that gives a string representation of a leader card.
    LeadersHand
    Cli component that gives a string representation of the player's leaders hand.
    MainTitle
    Cli component that renders the main title.
    Market
    Cli component that gives a string representation of the market.
    Menu
    Cli component that renders a menu.
    Menu.Entry
     
    ProductionSet
    Cli component that gives a string representation of multiple productions.
    Resource
    Cli component that represents the resources as bold and colored strings.

    Cli component that gives a string representation of multiple resource containers.
